                    <p>Choose from our top-quality and high-standard catalog offering the best instruments money can buy!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 mt-4 mt-lg-0 aos-init" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="150">
                <div class="box">
                    <span>Step 02</span>
                    <h4>Make an order</h4>
                    <p>Pick your gear and make an order with our easy and approacable platform. We guarantee the best prices in the market!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 mt-4 mt-lg-0 aos-init" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
                <div class="box">
                    <span>Step 03</span>
                    <h4>Get your order in 24h</h4>
                    <p>We believe in awesome customer service and in fast and high-quality delivery. Get your order in 24 hours only!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</section>

